Wednesday, October 21, 1998

MERIT DOCKET

98-1695. State v. Ratliff.

Clermont App. No. CA98-01-002. On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that no conflict exists. This cause is therefore dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resniok, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
